<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="filename" content="lingxi_shopping_assistant.html">
    <title>灵犀导购助理 - 视觉修复版</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        primary: '#7C8CFF',
                        accent: '#B8A8FF',
                        pageBg: '#F8FAFD',
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;
            background-color: #E2E8F0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* 严格限制 iPhone 尺寸 */
        .iphone-frame {
            width: 375px;
            height: 812px;
            background-color: #F8FAFD;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-radius: 50px;
            border: 12px solid #1E293B;
            box-shadow: 0 40px 100px -20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.3);
        }

        .chat-content {
            flex: 1;
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding: 16px;
            padding-bottom: 120px;
            scrollbar-width: none;
        }
        .chat-content::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

        .bubble-container {
            max-width: 75%;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .ai-bubble {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border: 1px solid rgba(124, 140, 255, 0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(124, 140, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 4px 16px 16px 16px;
        }

        .user-bubble {
            background: #F3F4F6;
            border-radius: 16px 4px 16px 16px;
        }

        .bottom-nav {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-top: 1px solid #F1F5F9;
            padding: 12px 16px env(safe-area-inset-bottom);
        }

        .nav-header {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #F1F5F9;
            height: 60px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* 头像修复：强制圆形和尺寸 */
        .avatar-box {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            overflow: hidden;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            background: #EEF2FF;
            border: 1px solid #E0E7FF;
        }

        .quick-btn {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #7C8CFF;
            font-weight: 500;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="iphone-frame">
        <!-- 顶部导航 -->
        <header class="nav-header flex items-center justify-between px-4 pt-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 w-20">
                <i data-lucide="chevron-left" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                <span class="text-[13px] text-slate-500">店铺</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center flex-1">
                <h1 class="text-[15px] font-bold text-slate-800 tracking-tight">灵犀导购助理</h1>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
                    <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full"></span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-medium">在线中</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-3 w-20">
                <i data-lucide="settings" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i>
                <button class="text-[11px] font-bold text-primary bg-primary/10 px-2 py-1 rounded-md transition-all active:scale-95">人工</button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- 聊天区域 -->
        <div class="chat-content flex flex-col gap-6">
            
            <!-- AI Welcome: 头像已修复 -->
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="avatar-box">
                    <img src="https://img.pixso.cn/ai/2023/11/15/65548dbbb3e85.png" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="灵犀助手" onerror="this.src='https://api.dicebear.com/7.x/bottts-neutral/svg?seed=lingxi'">
                </div>
                <div class="bubble-container flex flex-col gap-1.5">
                    <span class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 font-medium ml-1">灵犀店长</span>
                    <div class="ai-bubble p-3 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
                        亲爱的 88VIP，晚上好！我是店长的专属AI助理。✨<br><br>
                        店铺目前全场 <span class="text-primary font-bold">满200减20</span>，现货48小时内发货哦~ 请问有什么您可以帮您的？
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- User Query: 图片已修复，内容符合度假风穿搭语义 -->
            <div class="flex flex-col items-end gap-2">
                <div class="bubble-container flex flex-col items-end gap-2">
                    <div class="w-[160px] h-[220px] overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm bg-slate-50">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1496747611176-843222e1e57c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=400" 
                             class="w-full h-full object-cover block" alt="法式度假风参考图">
                    </div>
                    <div class="user-bubble p-3 text-[14px] text-slate-700 leading-normal">
                        下周去三亚玩，想找一套类似图片里的度假风穿搭。🌴
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- AI Response: 头像已修复 -->
            <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5">
                <div class="avatar-box">
                    <img src="https://img.pixso.cn/ai/2023/11/15/65548dbbb3e85.png" class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="灵犀助手">
                </div>
                <div class="bubble-container flex flex-col gap-1.5">
                    <span class="text-[11px] text-slate-400 font-medium ml-1">灵犀店长</span>
                    <div class="ai-bubble p-3 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
                        收到！正在为您识别图片风格...<br><br>
                        您发的是一套 <span class="font-bold text-primary">法式度假风裙装</span>。为了给您推荐最合身的尺码，请问您的身高体重大概是多少呢？
                    </div>
                    <!-- 快捷输入 -->
                    <div class="flex gap-2 mt-1 px-1">
                        <button class="quick-btn shadow-sm active:bg-slate-50">160cm/50kg</button>
                        <button class="quick-btn shadow-sm active:bg-slate-50">165cm/60kg</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- 底部输入栏 -->
        <footer class="bottom-nav">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5 shrink-0 text-slate-400">
                    <i data-lucide="plus" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    <i data-lucide="camera" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 h-10 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center px-4">
                    <span class="text-[14px] text-slate-400">请输入或按住说话...</span>
                </div>
                <button class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white shrink-0 shadow-lg shadow-primary/20">
                    <i data-lucide="send" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
        </footer>

        <!-- iPhone 装饰件 -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-32 h-6 bg-black rounded-b-2xl z-20"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-32 h-1 bg-slate-300 rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            lucide.createIcons();
            // 自动滚动到底部
            const chatContent = document.querySelector('.chat-content');
            chatContent.scrollTop = chatContent.scrollHeight;
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
